        <updateDate>2021-02-17T15:03:13Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Election Fraud Prevention Act</b></p> <p>This bill requires each state, in order to receive certain election assistance funds, to prohibit the knowing collection and transmission of a ballot in a federal election that was mailed to another person (commonly referred to as ballot harvesting), with exceptions. </p>]]></text>
      </summary>
    </summaries>
